# Docker build context = this module root (see ee/Dockerfile). Two jobs:
# 1) SECRETS never enter the image context — ee/deploy/tokens.json is a real token file the
#    compose quickstart tells operators to create. Excluding it here is the only reliable
#    guard (deleting in a later RUN layer would still leave it in the copied layer).
# 2) Keep the context small: build trees and node_modules are gigabytes of noise.
# NOTE: keep the explicit tokens.json line even though the *.json glob covers it — the
# explicit rule is the security guard; the glob is only hygiene and may be edited freely.
ee/deploy/tokens.json
ee/deploy/*.json
target
ee/target
frontend/node_modules
